text: Panarakuum Island also known as Panarakiim Island is an island in Milne Bay Province of Papua New Guinea.Panarakuum Island: Papua New Guinea National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency, Bethesda, MD, USA It is in the Conflict Group archipelago, part of the Louisiade Archipelago in the Solomon Sea. ==References== Category:Islands of Milne Bay Province Category:Louisiade Archipelago Category:Uninhabited islands of Papua New Guinea
title: Panarakuum Island
